<ContentCollab
  linkId="content-creators__presentations_and_workshops"
  media="Presentations & Workshops"
>
  <p slot="after_h2" class="utility_classes__center">
    Our presentations and workshops inspire & educate singles!
  </p>
  <p slot="paragraphs">
    In-person or virtual presentations and workshops are a great way to engage
    your stakeholders, connect with your customers, and grow your brand. In the
    past, we've partnered with small businesses, support groups, non-profits,
    and many other types of organizations to do help them do just that.
  </p>
  <p slot="paragraphs">
    Some of our most popular topics are listed below. If you have any ideas of
    your own, let us know!
  </p>
  <p slot="paragraphs">
    We've been working with divorced women for decades, and we'd be happy to
    share our experiences and insights with you!
  </p>
  <h3 slot="topics">
    Presentation & <span class="utility_classes__clean_break_on_wrap">Workshop Topics</span>
  </h3>
  <ul slot="topics">
    <li>
      <img src="../../assets/icons/heart-50.png" loading="lazy" />
      <span>Online Dating 101 For Divorc√©es</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <img src="../../assets/icons/heart-50.png" loading="lazy" />
      <span>Dating Secrets From A Certified Master Coach</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <img src="../../assets/icons/heart-50.png" loading="lazy" />
      <span>Online Dating Profile Workshops</span>
    </li>

    <li>
      <img src="../../assets/icons/heart-50.png" loading="lazy" />
      <span>Guided Book Discussions </span>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <FlexColumn slot="previous_collabs">
    <ImageModal
      imgLinkFullScreen="#discover_what_makes_you_attractive"
      imgIdFullScreen="discover_what_makes_you_attractive"
      imgClass="content-creators__book_discussion_flyer"
      imgSource="/assets/images/ContentCollabWhatMakesYouAttractive.png"
      imgAlt="Promotional flyer for a guided book discussion of Marie Forleo's Make Every Man Want You."
      imgLinkThumbnail="#discover_what_makes_you_attractive_thumbnail"
      imgIdThumbnail="discover_what_makes_you_attractive_thumbnail"
    />
    <ImageModal
      imgLinkFullScreen="#easing_the_stress"
      imgIdFullScreen="easing_the_stress"
      imgClass="content-creators__book_discussion_flyer"
      imgSource="/assets/images/ContentCollabEasingTheStress.png"
